{"tid":2232175,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"回應警察隊員佐級協會投訴 郭家麒: 我的言論公道自在人心","createTime":"2020-10-06T08:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T08:21:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a01cfcd0588adecf95e284826402336e7608891c","tid":2232175,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉去信醫委會，投訴本身是醫生的公民黨立法會議員郭家麒，涉嫌違反專業操守及醫德。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒回應，香港人擁有言論自由，他的言論公道自在人心，希望警隊不要忘記作為公僕，要服務市民而非打壓市民。<br />\n<br />\n協會在信中指出，留意到郭家麒在網上一再惡意中傷及羞辱警員，行為與醫者應有的崇高道德標準相違背。信中又指，政客的言行帶有政治取向，甚至為不可告人的政治目的辦事早已不是新鮮事。然而，作為一名醫生理應具備更崇高的專業操守標準，讓公眾對醫生的專業能力和誠信保持信心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553292-20201006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553292-20201006.htm&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKBUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=10a1b7c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553292-20201006.htm&h=612d34c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553292-20201006.htm</a>"},{"pid":"542a0b5da21664f7e82a7d2c5ffc29f3f76e4024","tid":2232175,"uid":55043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"泛呢班垃圾回應永遠都係咁軟弱"},{"pid":"f27366bc1bdcd5efbc7dc291a7cd02964bdea4a4","tid":2232175,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"542a0b5da21664f7e82a7d2c5ffc29f3f76e4024","tid":2232175,"uid":55043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:17:33.000Z","msg":"泛呢班垃圾回應永遠都係咁軟弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"屌泛民？<br />\n你走先我幫你頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3575beea75ef23aaa85dc4ff2de5e3afea400a","tid":2232175,"uid":91317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"屌應該話專業失德呢D你地警察就最專業啦"}]}